{"about_the_game":"<strong>GUILTY</strong> is a first-person psychological horror game.<br><br><strong>STORYLINE</strong><br>Play as <i>Peter</i>, an ex-military, and discover what your past hides. Access your unconscious to remember the traumatic and most terrifying memories that are hidden. Find out what happened to <i>Linda</i>, Peter's wife. A traumatic past that gives you a sense of guilt. What would you do if past trauma no longer allowed you to have a normal life?<br><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br>With just the help of a flashlight, explore a national park and a terrifying house inside your mind to relive your traumas and face them. Solve puzzles to gain access to important areas. Explore, remember, run and survive. Try to overcome your fears.<br><br>Collect memory fragments to access your unconscious.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/Dissolve.gif?t=1663282293\" /><br><br>Explore caves where a dark ritual is taking place.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/Cave2.gif?t=1663282293\" /><br><br>Find out what's real and what's hallucination.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/Ghost.gif?t=1663282293\" /><br><br>Be tormented by darkness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/Kitchen.gif?t=1663282293\" /><br><br>Explore the house to find levers that unlock access to restricted areas.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/Lever.gif?t=1663282293\" /><br><br>Discover the correct way to position the mannequins to progress in the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/Mane.gif?t=16